==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Allodial
<hw>Al*lo"di*al</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[LL.
<ets>allodialis</ets>, fr. <ets>allodium</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>allodial</ets>. See <er>Allodium</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Law)</fld>
<def>Pertaining to allodium; freehold; free of rent or service; held
independent of a lord paramount; -- opposed to <ant>feudal</ant>;
<as>as, <ex>allodial</ex> lands; <ex>allodial</ex> system.</as></def>
<rj><au>Blackstone.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Allodial</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Allodial
<hw>Al*lo"di*al</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Anything held allodially.</def>
<rj><au>W. Coxe.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Allodialism</ent>⟦br⟧
